# Mappings
map d scroll half-down
map <C-d> scroll half-down
map u scroll half-up
map <C-u> scroll half-up
map f scroll full-down
map <C-f> scroll full-down
map b scroll full-up
map <C-b> scroll full-up

map <C-n> navigate next
map <C-p> navigate previous

map P snap_to_page
map p snap_to_page

map gF display_link
map gf follow

unmap t
map td toggle_page_mode
map ti toggle_inputbar
map ts toggle_statusbar

map <C-l> reload
